<p>13 April 1915<br/>Tuesday</p>
<p>Turn the whole lot into one unit   &amp;  call ourselves the 4th Inf Bgde Details A B C   &amp;  D companies.<br/>Pitch camp all in one spot near the old Brigade Headquarters which is used as orderly Room   &amp;  Officers Mess</p>
<p>1915 April 14<br/>Wednesday</p>
<p>Go on a route march to the first Tower a distance of about 3 miles from camp along one of the roads built by Napoleon during his occupation of Egypt.</p>
